      "span_text": "For decreasing a/L, the effect of the accuracy in c t on the results is expected to become even smaller. The contribution to the error of Σ stat A induced by the uncertainty in the coupling u (which can be estimated with the aid of the one-loop result ln(2)γ 0 for the derivative of σ stat A with respect to u) is negligible compared to the statistical error of Σ stat A."
